my config files for suckless software
=====================================

Installation
------------
Run the following commands:

    git clone https://github.com/lazarescu1/suckless.git
    cd suckless
    cd dwm && make clean install
    cd dmenu && make clean install
    cd slstatus && make clean install


Running dwm & slstatus
----------------------
Add the following lines to your .xinitrc file to start dwm with startx:

    exec dwm &
    exec slstatus
    

More info
---------
See

    https://dwm.suckless.org
    https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu
    https://tools.suckless.org/slstatus

for more info about dwm, dmenu and slstatus (plus other software).
